title: 1993 Ýokary Liga
text:
The 1993 Turkmenistan Higher League (<a href="%C3%9Dokary%20Liga">Ýokary Liga</a>) season was the second season of <a href="Turkmenistan">Turkmenistan</a>'s professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> league. Its first round started March 27, 1993, and finished October 3, 1993, and the second round was between November 3 and December 4.
